🇺🇦➡️ In just 24 hours since May 1, the air defense units of the "South" group of forces neutralized 399 air targets:
▫️ 93 "Shahed";
▫️ 21 reconnaissance UAVs;
▫️ 285 attack drones of the "Molniya" and "Lancet" types.

