❗️During April 2026, the air defense of the Defense Forces of 🇺🇦Ukraine destroyed more than 57,000 aerial targets:
▪️ 69 Kh-101 cruise missiles;
▪️ 7 Iskander-M/KN-23 ballistic missiles;
▪️ 8 Kalibr cruise missiles;
▪️ 4 Kh-59/69 guided air-launched missiles;
▪️ 5 Iskander-K cruise missiles;
▪️ 4,861 Shahed-type attack UAVs;
▪️ 1,065 reconnaissance UAVs;
▪️ 51,110 UAVs of other types.

